## Conventions

- Secrets in `.env` only; see `.env.example`
- `.gitignore`: `/vault/` and `/models/` (root only) — never `app/vault/` or `app/models/` (ADR 0002)
- Celery tasks use `worker_session()` (ADR 0001)
- Alembic migrations under `alembic/versions/`
- User prefers German; README DE+EN; Roadmap/ADRs auf Deutsch
- Eine Story → eine PR; CHANGELOG unter `[Unreleased]`
- **Kein Custom-n8n-Node** (ADR 0004); REST + `examples/n8n/` für Power-User

## Key files

- `docker-compose.yml` — api, worker, db, redis; `docker-compose.consumer.yml` (E20-1), `.vps.yml` (E20-2)
- `scripts/install.sh`, `scripts/deploy-vps.sh`, `scripts/update.sh`, `scripts/doctor.sh`
- `app/main.py` — health, API + UI mount
- `app/db/session.py` — `get_db()`, `worker_session()`
- `app/ui/router.py` — `/dashboard`, `/ask`, `/notes`, `/settings`, `/setup`, `/api/ui/*`
